The '''Battle of Abridon''' may refer to several of a series of battles on that planet.
*The [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance's]] '''[[Uprising on Abridon|attempt]]''' to drive the Empire off Abridon.
*The '''[[Massacre on Abridon]]''': the Empire took back the planet under the command of General [[Brenn Tantor]].
*The Alliance's '''[[Liberation of Abridon|successful campaign]]''' to drive the Empire off-world.
